    <item>
      <title>Canon AI 影印机在港亮相    AI 处理扫描文件、AI Genie 2 套件加快商业文件处理效率</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/11/canon-imageforce/ai/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=canon-imageforce</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/11/canon-imageforce/ai/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Lawton</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Jul 2025 11:40:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>人工智能</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1316208</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Canon 今日在尖沙咀举行「THINK BIG – Automate. Optimize. Innovate.」展示活动，首次在港公开介绍具备 AI 功能的全新影印机 imageFORCE 系列，并同步介绍升级版 AI Genie 2 解决方案，展示智能办公设备如何应对企业在数码化与效率管理方面的实际需求。这些方案针对文档处理、分类归档、招募管理、帐务自动化等流程进行改良，目标是简化日常操作并提升生产力。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06975-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06975-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06975.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06972-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06972-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06972.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06969-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06969-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06969.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canon 今次展示的 imageFORCE 多功能影印机系列，加入多项 AI 辅助功能，协助企业加快资料处理。这系列机种配备 AI Genie Connector，可以即时辨识影印文件内容，并自动分类及建立搜寻索引。用户扫描文件后，系统会自动分析内容，例如是否为发票、报表或合同，并将资料整理分类，减少手动归档时间，亦能提升档案处理准确度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07016-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07016-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07016.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07021-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07021-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07021.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲扫描文件后，识自动放入预先制好的资料夹，例如图中的单据就放入 Invoice&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07022-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07022-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07022.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07023-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07023-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07023.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲单据资料将由 OCR 辨识，以 AI 加强准确度，并可将数据自动入库&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;除了文件分类功能，imageFORCE 系列也整合多重资讯保安措施，包括使用者验证、扫描加密、列印管控与帐户权限设定。Canon 表示这系列机种使用新一代机械学习维修技术，能事前分析装置状况，预测所需保养时间，以降低停机机率。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07002-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07002-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07002.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07017-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07017-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07017.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07004-694x452.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="452" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07004-694x452.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07004-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06952-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06952-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06952.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲影印机 AI 功能更可向维护人员汇报打印机遇到的问题，让维护人员花更少时间处理&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;AI Genie 2 套件加快商业文件处理效率&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;另一焦点产品 AI Genie 2，作为 Canon 企业数码化方案的核心技术，强调协助企业在文件与流程管理上节省时间。这套系统利用 Agentic AI 与 Model Context Protocol（MCP）技术，能针对不同商业部门的实际需要，处理大量数据、建立分类逻辑并提出建议方案。AI Genie 2 透过自动学习能力，能分辨用户常见操作与指令，并将流程自动化，例如文件填表、分类、审核等作业。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07006-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07006-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07006.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06946-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06946-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06946.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07009-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07009-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07009-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07010-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07010-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07010-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲行销部门可输入要求， AI 便可自动从资料库取得数据分析，并为用户提供行销建议&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AI Genie 2 可应用于企业内多个部门，当中包括人力资源及财务管理。以人力资源部门为例，系统可根据履历内容自动分类求职者经历、能力及职位要求，缩短招聘流程。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07012-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07012-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc07012.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲AI 可连结资料库，为财务管理部门制作行销、财政分析报表，也可为 HR 部门分析求职者&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06949-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06949-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06949.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;同时，AI Genie 2 亦支援会计部门处理付款流程，例如可即时检查供应商发票与采购单是否一致，并协助处理应收帐项，建立格式统一的发票资料，输出报表。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canon 指出，新版 AI Genie 2 能够整合文件管理系统，协助企业从文件入手优化内部流程。AI 能自动判别文件种类和处理优先次序，并按部门标准分类或转交至其他部门继续跟进，让资料流动更流畅。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06955-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06955-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06955.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06966-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06966-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06966.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲用于保安用途，AI 应用于分析视像镜头所拍得的画面&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06943-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06943-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06943.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06945-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06945-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06945.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06944-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06944-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06944.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲利用 AI 及一系列感应器，管理房间预约、来宾登入等&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canon 今次展出的技术除针对企业办公效率外，亦配合近年企业强化 ESG（环境、社会及企业管治）需求，提供智能节能与数码化管理功能。Canon 方面预期，这些技术能协助企业更有效管理资源，并于转型过程中提升整体营运透明度与安全度。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1316232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06960-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06960-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06960.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
